--- .gitignore (原始)
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
.env

+++ .gitignore (修改后)
```
# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Build outputs
dist/
build/
*.js.map
*.tsbuildinfo

# Environment variables
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Logs
*.log

# Coverage reports
coverage/
htmlcov/
*.coverage

# IDE specific
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS specific
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Python cache (if any Python files exist in project)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp

# Package manager caches
.npm/
.yarn/
.pnpm-store/
```
